        class="spotlight style1 orient-right content-align-left image-position-center onscroll-image-fade-in"
      >
        <div class="content">
          <h2>Product Concept</h2>
          <p class="major">
            Based on our problem statement: ...to design a novel tangible user interface, which helps support the productivity, creativity, and well being of people who work or study in mobile environments.
            We created a tangible user interface (TUI) named Heartbeat Huggies.
          </p>
          <p class="major">
            We aim to promote productivity, creativity, and wellbeing through
            the sleep assistance of young children.
          </p>
        </div>
        
      </section>
